Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF\4c&HF75D03\3a&HFF\4a&H00\shad2\bord2}真是一尘不染令人平静的旋律
