Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF\4c&HF45B05\3a&HFF\4a&H00\shad2\bord2}就是因为能拉出如此美妙的音色
